{{Vgname|星之卡比64|ja=星のカービィ64|en=Kirby 64: The Crystal Shards|diff=yes}}是[[HAL研究所|HAL研究所]]开发、[[任天堂|任天堂]]2000年发行的[[平台游戏|平台游戏]]，对应[[任天堂64|任天堂64]]游戏机。游戏后来与[[Wii|Wii]]和[[Wii_U|Wii U]]的[[Virtual_Console|Virtual Console]]上再版。

日版游戏售出107万，美版游戏售出54万<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.the-magicbox.com/topten2.htm |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2008-05-22 |archive-date=2007-12-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071213230402/http://www.the-magicbox.com/topten2.htm |dead-url=no }} 1.07 million copies sold in Japan.</ref>。西方[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]统计的游戏汇总评分为77%<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/game/nintendo-64/kirby-64-the-crystal-shards |title=''Kirby 64: The Crystal Shards'' for Nintendo 64 Reviews |publisher=Metacritic |accessdate=2016-05-06 |archive-date=2013-02-04 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6EBTq9Of1?url=http://www.metacritic.com/game/nintendo-64/kirby-64-the-crystal-shards |dead-url=no }}</ref>，日本杂志《[[Fami通|Fami通]]》打出32/40分<ref>{{cite web|date=March 16, 2000|url=http://ign64.ign.com/articles/076/076678p1.html|title=Rating a Fat Blob|publisher=IGN|access-date=2016-05-06|archive-date=2012-02-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120205072247/http://ign64.ign.com/articles/076/076678p1.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

